<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="D" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Discontented" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Discontented,</orth> dissatisfied, out of humour: <bibl n="shak. jn 4.2.127" default="NO" valid="yes">John IV, 2, 127</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. jn 5.1.8" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 1, 8</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r2 3.3.63" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 III, 3, 63</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 3.1.163" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A III, 1, 163</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 4.2.36" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 IV, 2, 36</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 4.4.312" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 4, 312</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 5.1.7" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 1, 7</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h8 3.2.91" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 III, 2, 91</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cor 1.1.115" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. I, 1, 115</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cor 5.1.44" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 1, 44</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tim 3.5.115" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. III, 5, 115</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ant 2.6.6" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. II, 6, 6</bibl>. <cit><quote>here's another d. paper,</quote> <bibl n="shak. oth 5.2.314" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. V, 2, 314</bibl></cit> (a letter full of dissatisfaction).
